review_blob: The bottle is big and fancy looking. The beer its self is a bit less impressing on the look in a glass- brownish and unclear with almost no foam. Does not smell much but has nice fruity taste. Its quite sweet with low carbonation.
beer_name: Cigar City Guava Grove Farmhouse Ale

review_blob: If you like light, watery beer, you might like it. I do not and it tastes for me a little bit like chicken soup.
